body_html: core/ops/ops.pbtxt defines some expected attributes for the Reshape Op, which includes one called "Tshape". When the Op executes, it expects to find the desired output shape in its corresponding graph Node, but it's not there. It appears that the graph has been constructed without it, or somehow it got stripped prior to execution. Perhaps with this hint you can figure out what's going wrong.
